com.github.dandelion.core.asset.cache.spi
Interface AssetCache

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractAssetCache, MemoryAssetCache
public interface AssetCache

SPI for all implementation of AssetCache.

Dandelion provides one out-of-the-box service provider:

  • MemoryAssetCache that uses a simple HashMap for in-memory caching.

Since:
0.10.0
Author:
Romain Lespinasse, Thibault Duchateau
